wdi2-SL.TLF.0714.WK.TM.def: Average working hours of children working only refers to the average weekly working hours of those children who are involved in economic activity and not attending school.
wdi2-SL.TLF.0714.WK.TM.name: Average working hours of children, working only, ages 7-14
wdi2-SL.TLF.0714.WK.TM.source: Understanding Children's Work project based on data from ILO, UNICEF and the World Bank.
